OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784135919
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force in parts
OL,4,Cof Devon
OL,6,FA temporary hosepipe ban has been
OL,7,Fintroduced in Mid Devon and parts of
OL,8,FEast Devon due to the recent heatwaves.
OL,10,FThe restrictions come into force from
OL,11,Fmidday on Tuesday (14 July).
OL,13,FThe company says it's due to
OL,14,F"exceptionally high levels of demand
OL,15,Fin the area" and advises customers to
OL,16,Ffollow the restrictions immediately to
OL,17,Fhelp protect water supplies during
OL,18,Fthis current spell of very hot and dry
OL,19,Fweather.
OL,21,FThe towns and areas covered by the ban:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
