OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784135919
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force in parts
OL,4,Cof Devon
OL,6,FWater that is used from another
OL,7,Fsource, such as a water butt or other
OL,8,Frecycled water storage system, are
OL,9,Falso exempt from the ban.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
